* text=auto eol=lf

*.blade.php diff=html
*.css diff=css
*.html diff=html
*.md diff=markdown
*.php diff=php

/.github export-ignore
CHANGELOG.md export-ignore
.styleci.yml export-ignore

# 設置默認行為，如果 core.autocrlf 未設置
* text=auto

# 明確聲明應該標準化的文本文件
*.php text
*.css text
*.js text
*.html text
*.md text
*.yml text
*.json text

# 聲明二進制文件，不應進行任何轉換
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.zip binary
*.pdf binary
